description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Beginner Flexibility Routine V2! (FOLLOW ALONG)' from the channel Tom Merrick.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
